OL,3,CInjured and bereaved call for action
OL,4,Cto improve safety on London transport
OL,6,FPeople who have been injured or
OL,7,Fbereaved by incidents on the Transport
OL,8,Ffor London network have gathered in
OL,9,FWestminster to call for better safety.
OL,11,FFigures revealed on average 21 people
OL,12,Fa month have fallen between the train
OL,13,Fand the platform on the London
OL,14,FUnderground between 2014 and 2023.
OL,16,FA TfL Heath and Safety report also
OL,17,Ffound 86 people died or were seriously
OL,18,Finjured in bus collisions in the last
OL,19,Fthree months of 2023-24.
