OL,3,CInjured and bereaved call for action
OL,4,Cto improve safety on London transport
OL,6,FCampaigners want urgent government
OL,7,Faction to ensure TfL addresses safety
OL,8,Fconcerns and a statutory duty to be
OL,9,Fintroduced that requires more
OL,10,Ftransparency after deaths, injuries or
OL,11,Fnear misses on the network.
OL,13,FSarah de Lagarde is among those
OL,14,Flooking for change. She was struck by
OL,15,Ftwo London Underground trains while
OL,16,Ftravelling on the Northern Line,
OL,17,Fresulting in the amputation of her
OL,18,Fright arm and right leg.
OL,20,FShe said the fact that she survived
OL,21,Fwas "nothing short of a miracle".
