OL,3,CInjured and bereaved call for action
OL,4,Cto improve safety on London transport
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News London, Ms de
OL,7,FLargarde said: "I was very able-bodied
OL,8,Fbefore and within 24 hours I've become
OL,9,Fdisabled for life ... my message is
OL,10,Freally to raise awareness that these
OL,11,Fincidents happen way more often than
OL,12,FTfL would like us to believe."
OL,14,FThe mother of two, who describes
OL,15,Fherself as '80 per cent human, 20 per
OL,16,Fcent robot', added that she felt
OL,17,F"disappointed" and "not heard" by
OL,18,FTfL's response to her case.
