OL,3,CInjured and bereaved call for action
OL,4,Cto improve safety on London transport
OL,6,FShe said: "It seems customary for TfL
OL,7,Fto push the responsibility onto the
OL,8,Fcommuter and I believe that 'Please
OL,9,FMind the Gap' is not enough to protect
OL,10,Fcommuters.
OL,12,F"I worry about a decaying network that
OL,13,Fis in dire need of innovation and I
OL,14,Fbelieve the further we go on like
OL,15,Fthis, the more people will get
OL,16,Fseriously injured of lose their lives."
OL,18,FKathleen Finnegan died after being hit
OL,19,Fby a double-decker bus at Victoria
OL,20,FStation earlier this year.
