OL,3,CInjured and bereaved call for action
OL,4,Cto improve safety on London transport
OL,6,FHer friend, Sarah Sivas, told ITV
OL,7,FNews: " I think there's quite a big PR
OL,8,Foperation to try and present what they
OL,9,Fwant to present.
OL,11,F"They say safety is our number one
OL,12,Fpriority it's what we see in every
OL,13,Fpiece of information that they publish.
OL,15,F"But it doesn't reflect in how they
OL,16,Fbehave towards people who are bereaved.
