OL,3,CInjured and bereaved call for action
OL,4,Cto improve safety on London transport
OL,6,F"They need to think and listen to what
OL,7,Fwe're saying because it could in fact
OL,8,Fimprove things for them and it could
OL,9,Fimprove things for London transport
OL,10,Fusers."
OL,12,FLilli Matson, TfL's Chief Safety,
OL,13,FHealth and Environment Officer, said
OL,14,Fdeaths and serious incidents on the
OL,15,Ftransport network are "devastating".
