OL,3,CInjured and bereaved call for action
OL,4,Cto improve safety on London transport
OL,6,FShe added: "We are committed to
OL,7,Flearning from every incident and use a
OL,8,Frigorous evidence-based approach to
OL,9,Fthis, using data and incident reports
OL,10,Fto put in place changes through
OL,11,Ftargeted programmes that make the
OL,12,Ftransport network safer for everyone.
OL,14,F"Accurate reporting and transparency
OL,15,Fare a vital part of our industry-
OL,16,Fleading approach to safety and we are
OL,17,Fcommitted to making data publicly
OL,18,Favailable, including through our
OL,19,Fwebsite.
