OL,6,F"We recognise that serious incidents
OL,7,Fon the network should never happen and
OL,8,Fwe are determined to address this by
OL,9,Flistening to the experiences of those
OL,10,Fwho are affected and taking
OL,11,Fappropriate action to keep people
OL,12,Fsafe."
OL,14,FSadiq Khan: "I was with the TfL
OL,15,Fmanagement team yesterday expressing
OL,16,Fmy concern about any sort of victim
OL,17,Fblaming.
